    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自动战斗+集换式卡牌游戏的创新融合！成为冒险者佳缪，在数个充满未知的星界中穿梭。通过高度自由化的卡组，召唤异界的怪兽协助你的征服之路！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏特色：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 极高自由度的卡组构筑：在开始冒险前，你可以选择并编辑独一无二的卡组，冒险过程中也能不断获得新的卡牌，动态调整卡组以适应复杂多变的战斗环境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319720/extras/c90bb871a64629dde8b116edff1b3ace.poster.avif?t=1762499495\" width=800 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319720/extras/c90bb871a64629dde8b116edff1b3ace.webm?t=1762499495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319720/extras/c90bb871a64629dde8b116edff1b3ace.mp4?t=1762499495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 即时的自动战斗：在时间冻结期间，场上的单位均无法行动，此时可以使用卡牌实现多种效果。你需要选择合适的时机进行时间冻结，以最大化自己的优势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 丰富多样的物品：冒险中你能够获得多种物品，它们均有十分重要的作用，合理选择物品搭配，与卡组配合实现最大收益。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319720/extras/17eab1f2fe6c89f85b18bf63c7888365.poster.avif?t=1762499495\" width=800 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319720/extras/17eab1f2fe6c89f85b18bf63c7888365.webm?t=1762499495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319720/extras/17eab1f2fe6c89f85b18bf63c7888365.mp4?t=1762499495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 自由探索：在网状的地图中自由行动，不受前进方向束缚。但是注意，游戏难度会随着行动轮数的增加而不断增强！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319720/extras/a6b30805f3ab938d127ecec372f2df95.poster.avif?t=1762499495\" width=800 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319720/extras/a6b30805f3ab938d127ecec372f2df95.webm?t=1762499495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319720/extras/a6b30805f3ab938d127ecec372f2df95.mp4?t=1762499495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
